{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"33":{"eng-name":"Etiquette","ara-name":"كتاب الأدب"}},"section_detail":{"33":{"hadithnumber_first":3657,"hadithnumber_last":3826,"arabicnumber_first":3657,"arabicnumber_last":3826}}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":3714,"arabicnumber":3714,"text":"حدثنا علي بن محمد، حدثنا وكيع، عن عكرمة بن عمار، عن اياس بن سلمة بن الاكوع، عن ابيه، قال قال رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم \" يشمت العاطس ثلاثا فما زاد فهو مزكوم","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Daif"}],"reference":{"book":33,"hadith":58},"chapter":{"id":20,"ara-name":"باب تَشْمِيتِ الْعَاطِسِ","eng-name":"Replying to one who sneezes","isFirstHadith":false}}]}